overview:
Custom Soft is an offshore software development company located in Pune, India. This company offers software services including software product development, testing, maintenance, enhancement etc.

We have expert .Net, Java, VB, C#, ASP.Net, PHP and Delphi programmers team who assure us the delivery of best and quality software products for retail, hotel, insurance, healthcare and logistic business including the ERP, CRM, SCM, DMS and CMS software solutions.

Custom Soft is providing software outsourcing services to many clients and multinational companies from USA,UK, Australia, Canada and India.
